{"tid":765803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"食環署瑞和街執法 惹燒臘檔職員不滿 附近商戶亦加入戰團 警方持盾牌到場調停","createTime":"2018-08-03T05:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-03T06:56:46.000Z","uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a3066ed38ee192b7180a7d503d6824ad227fee7e","tid":765803,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:19:58.000Z","msg":"下午1時許，食環署人員到觀塘瑞和街執法，其間懷疑一間燒臘檔有物件阻街，於是採取行動，但燒臘檔職員不服，與食環署人員發生爭執，附近店舖有職員亦加入戰團，爆粗大罵食環署人員，事件引來大批途人圍觀。警方接報後派出手持盾牌的警員到場調查，經調停後協助食環署人員離開，事件中無人受傷，無人被捕。"},{"pid":"b9e5ef1162f7d86f97c746accd279dfd15e366c9","tid":765803,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T05:21:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警方接報後派出手持盾牌的警員到場調查</span><br />\n又盾牌,下次不如出速龍小隊啦"},{"pid":"797dc7d73e991b2c094b5e5abe034209bcd11fd6","tid":765803,"uid":193070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"都未出水炮車射嘢，試水溫槍有冇用嘛"},{"pid":"26353ab7b30872695d1cc78affea6d0910901fe5","tid":765803,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797dc7d73e991b2c094b5e5abe034209bcd11fd6","tid":765803,"uid":193070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:45:22.000Z","msg":"都未出水炮車射嘢，試水溫槍有冇用嘛"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:50:26.000Z","msg":"食環都可以自己出洗地車<br />\n一嘢射入去燒臘檔幫佢洗地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13d1cfe7b603385af2678adafa6f9599f99d71e","tid":765803,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-03T06:51:10.000Z","msg":"又可以打市民 爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9eb624c32546d69c2b9bb7293cababd70e1923ce","tid":765803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26353ab7b30872695d1cc78affea6d0910901fe5","tid":765803,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"797dc7d73e991b2c094b5e5abe034209bcd11fd6","tid":765803,"uid":193070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,